# Toot.exe

Ever feel lonely on your computer? 
Well not any more! Toot.exe is here for you!

Toot.exe is a "Pal Program". It can add a variety of pals to your computer screen.

Currently, only the dancing Toothless memes are in here, but future features include additional characters.

Music Toot
![alt text](docs/MusicRocker.png)

## Features
- Add a number of Toothless Characters to your screen
- Move and reposition them however you want
- No spyware! Imagine that? A pal program that doesn't sell your info!

## Installation

To use this program, you'll need to have Python and pip installed on your machine. If you don't have them installed, you can follow these instructions:

1. Install Python: [Python Installation Guide](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
2. Install pip: [pip Installation Guide](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing/)

Once you have Python and pip installed, you can proceed with the following steps:

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Open a terminal or command prompt and navigate to the project directory.
3. Install the required dependencies by running the following command:
    ```
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    ```

## Usage

To run the program, execute main.py


